subsection_analysis.refined_text: : These contain fields that you can select and fill in. •.

You can complete the forms by entering information and adding your signatures. Acrobat also allows you to send your completed forms to others and securely save them in Adobe cloud storage. It could be a paper form or PDF that hasn’t been optimized for form filling. The Fill & Sign tool automatically detects the form fields like text fields, comb fields, checkboxes, and radio buttons. You can manually add text and other symbols anywhere on the form using the Fill & Sign tool if required. : These do not have interactive fields.
See Create a form from an existing document .
Creates the PDF so that it conforms to the selected ISO standard for long-term preservation of electronic documents.
These non-interactive forms are called flat forms.
